description:
This is a 37 minute workout called '35 MIN FULL BODY PILATES WORKOUT FOR BEGINNERS || No Equipment' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Restoration Wave and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
